Scotty Beckett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scotty_Beckett 0 Scott Hastings "Scotty" Beckett (October 4, 1929 – May 10, 1968) was an American actor. He began his career as a child actor in the Our Gang shorts and later costarred on Rocky Jones, Space Ranger.
